 93→\section{The Koide Formula as Energy Balance}
 94→\label{sec:koide_algebra}
 95→%======================================================================
 96→
 97→\subsection{Charges, not masses}
 98→
 99→The fundamental variable is the signed mass charge $\zch = z_0 + z_i 
100→\in \mathbb{R}$, with the physical mass $m = \zch^2 \geq 0$.
